'''Ice barges''' were self-contained [[Repulsorcraft/Legends|repulsorcraft]] used to traverse snow-covered terrain.<ref name="DFRSB">''[[Dark Force Rising Sourcebook]]''</ref> They were used by the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] to travel across the inhospitable wastes of [[Csilla/Legends|Csilla]], between cities.<ref name="FHII">''[[The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic II: Refugee]]''</ref> The [[Tolo]]s of [[Toloran]] also had an ice barge named the ''[[Snow Nara]]'' which was used for tourist purposes.<ref name="DFRSB" />

